    23

    51                                                 realtime        RESULT_PERIOD;
    52                                               
    53                                               
    54                                                 // reg             CLK_Out_i;
    55                                                 realtime        time_now;
    56                                                 reg             preparation_flag;

    66                                                 reg [WIDTH-1:0] sine[0:359];
    67                                               
    68                                                 int PPM;
    69                                               
    70                                               
    71                                                 assign CLK_Out = CLK_Out_i;
    72                                               
    73                                               
    74                                                 integer i, j, k;
    75                                                 realtime               last_time;  // Require time data type
    76                                               
    77                                                 reg      [WIDTH - 1:0] sin_0                                [0:359];
    78                                                 reg      [WIDTH - 1:0] sin_90                               [0:359];
    79                                                 reg      [WIDTH - 1:0] sin_180                              [0:359];

    98                                               
    99                                               `ifdef THREE_CLKS
    100                                              
    101                                                 Clk_Gen Clk_gen_U(
    102

    112                                                ////////////////////////////////////////////////
    113                                                //////////////// SIGN OF SIN WAVES //////////////
    114                                                ////////////////////////////////////////////////
    115                                              
    116             1                   20836700       always @* begin
    117             1                   10712027         if (sin_sum >= THRESHOLD) CLK_Out_i = 1;
    118             1                   10124673         else CLK_Out_i = 0;
    119                                                end
    120                                              
    121                                              
    122             1                   75614580       always @* begin
    123             1                   38647317         if (sin_0[index] >= THRESHOLD) sign_0 = 1;
    124             1                   36967263         else sign_0 = 0;
    125                                                end
    126                                              
    127                                              
    128             1                   75614580       always @* begin
    129             1                   38647255         if (sin_45[index] >= THRESHOLD) sign_45 = 1;

    131                                                end
    132

    136             1                   36967391         else sign_90 = 0;
    137                                                end
    138

    143                                                end

    181                                                initial begin
    182             1                          1         i             = 0;
    183             1                          1         j             = 0;
    184             1                          1         k             = 0;
    185             1                          1         last_time     = 0;
    186             1                          1         T1            = 0;
    187                                                  // clk_filter_   = 0;
    188                                                  // clk_filter    = 0;
    189             1                          1         glitchF_found = 0;
    190             1                          1         glitchR_found = 0;
    191                                                end
    192                                              
    193                                              
    194                                                initial begin
    195             1                          1         forever begin
    196             1                     104983           @(posedge CLK);
    197             1                     104983           t1 = $realtime;
    198             1                     104983           @(posedge CLK);
    199             1                     104982           t2  = $realtime;
    200             1                     104982           T1  = t2 - t1;
    201             1                     104982           PPM = int'(((5 - (1 / T1)) / (5)) * (10 ** 6));
    202                                                  end
    203                                                end
    204                                              
    205                                              
    206                                                initial begin
    207             1                          1         forever begin
    208             1                     105091           @(negedge sign_0);
    209             1                     105091           t3 = $realtime;
    210             1                     105091           @(negedge sign_0);
    211             1                     105090           t4 = $realtime;
    212             1                     105090           T_ = t4 - t3;
    213                                                  end
    214                                                end
    215                                              
    216                                              
    217                                              
    218                                              
    219                                              
    220                                                initial begin
    221             1                          1         forever begin
    222             1                     105026           @(posedge CLK_Out_i);
    223             1                     105025           t5 = $realtime;
    224             1                     105025           @(posedge CLK_Out_i);
    225             1                     105025           t6 = $realtime;
    226             1                     105025           RESULT_PERIOD = t6 - t5;
    227                                                  end
    228                                                end
    229                                              
    230                                              
    231                                              
    232                                              
    233                                                reg clk_sin;
    234             1                          1       initial clk_sin = 0;
    235             1                  151107554       always #(((0.2 / 360) / 2)) clk_sin = ~clk_sin;
    235             2                  151107553     
    236                                              
    237                                              
    238                                              
    239                                                initial begin
    240                                              
    241             1                        360         do begin
    242             1                        360           preparation_flag = 1;
    243             1                        360           @(posedge clk_sin);
    244             1                        360           sin_0[i]   = sine[i];
    245             1                        360           sin_45[i]  = sine[(i+45)%360];
    246             1                        360           sin_90[i]  = sine[(i+90)%360];
    247             1                        360           sin_135[i] = sine[(i+135)%360];
    248             1                        360           sin_180[i] = sine[(i+180)%360];
    249             1                        360           sin_225[i] = sine[(i+225)%360];
    250             1                        360           sin_270[i] = sine[(i+270)%360];
    251             1                        360           sin_315[i] = sine[(i+315)%360];
    252             1                        360           i          = i + 1;
    253                                                  end while (i != 360);
    254             1                          1         i = 0;
    255             1                          1         preparation_flag = 0;
    256                                                end
    257                                              
    258                                              
    259                                              
    260                                              
    261             1                          1       initial clk_index = 0;
    262             1                  420079001       always #(0.0001) clk_index = ~clk_index;  //0.0002
    262             2                  420079000     
    263                                              
    264                                              
    265                                                ////////////////////////////////////////////////
    266                                                //////////////// INDEX CHANGE //////////////////
    267                                                ////////////////////////////////////////////////
    268                                              
    269             1                  210039500       always @(posedge clk_index) begin
    270             1                  210039500         time_now = $realtime - 0.2 * $floor($realtime / 0.2);  //T1 ---> change to T1
    271             1                  210039500         index    = integer'((time_now / 0.2) * 360) % 360;
    272                                                end
    273                                              
    274                                                ////////////////////////////////////////////////
    275                                                ////////////////////////////////////////////////

    279             1                   75666383       always @(*) begin
    280                                                  if (!preparation_flag) begin
    281                                              
    282                                                    case (Code[10:8])
    283                                              
    284                                                      3'b000: begin
    285             1                     865317               sin_sum  = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_45[index]  + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_0[index] )))      ;
    286                                                      end
    287                                              
    288                                                      3'b001: begin
    289             1                   15308162               sin_sum   = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_90[index]  + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_45[index] )))       ;
    290                                              
    291                                                      end
    292                                              
    293                                                      3'b010: begin
    294             1                   59078027               sin_sum  = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_135[index] + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_90[index] )))    ;
    295                                              
    296                                                      end
    297                                              
    298                                                      3'b011: begin
    299             1                    ***0***               sin_sum  = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_180[index]  + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_135[index] )))  ;
    300                                                 
    301                                                      end
    302                                              
    303                                                      3'b100: begin
    304             1                    ***0***               sin_sum  = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_225[index]  + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_180[index] )))  ;
    305                                              
    306                                                      end
    307                                              
    308                                                      3'b101: begin
    309             1                    ***0***               sin_sum  = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_270[index]  + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_225[index] )))  ;
    310                                              
    311                                                      end
    312                                              
    313                                                      3'b110: begin

    315                                              
    316                                                      end
    317                                              
    318                                                      3'b111: begin
    319             1                     414158               sin_sum  = ((Code[7:0]/255.0 * sin_0[index]  + ((255.0 - Code[7:0])/255.0 * sin_315[index] )))    ;
    320                                                   
    321                                                      end

    323                                              
    324                                                  end

    13                                                   if (~Rst_n) begin

    15                                                   end else begin
    16              1                     209965           current_period = $realtime() - previous_rising_edge;
    17              1                     209965           previous_rising_edge = $realtime();

    20

    22                                                 int PPM_value;
    23              1                          6       always @(current_period) begin

    26                                               
    27                                                  property PPM_check;

    52                                                   // constraint reset_c {
    53                                                   //     Reset_n dist {1'b1:/ 95 , 1'b0:/5 };
    54                                                   // }
    55                                               
    56                                               
    57                                                   //---------- MAC_DATAK_CONSTRAINT --------
    58                                                   constraint MAC_TX_Data_32c {
    59                                                     if (Data_post == 32'hBCBC_BCBC) {
    60                                                       MAC_TX_Data inside {[32'h0 : 32'hFFFF_FFFF]};
    61                                                     } else {
    62                                                       MAC_TX_Data == 32'hBCBC_BCBC;
    63                                                     }
    64                                               
    65                                                   }
    66                                               
    67                                               
    68                                               
    69                                                   constraint MAC_TX_Data_TSEQ {
    70                                                     if (Data_post == 32'hBCBC_BCBC) {
    71                                                       MAC_TX_Data == 32'h4A_4A_4A_4A;
    72                                                     } else {
    73                                                       MAC_TX_Data == 32'hBCBC_BCBC;
    74                                                     }
    75                                                   }
    76                                               
    77                                               
    78                                               
    79                                                   //---------- MAC_DATAK_CONSTRAINT ---------
    80                                                   constraint MAC_TX_DataK_32c {
    81                                                     if (Data_post != 32'hBCBC_BCBC) {
    82                                                       MAC_TX_DataK == 4'b1111;
    83                                                     } else {
    84                                                       MAC_TX_DataK == 4'b0000;
    85                                                     }
    86                                                   }
    87                                               
    88                                               
    89                                               
    90                                                   //------ MAC_DATA_En CONSTARINT------
    91                                                   constraint MAC_Data_En_c {
    92                                                     // MAC_Data_En dist {1'b1 :/ 95 , 1'b0:/ 5};
    93                                                     MAC_Data_En == 1'b1;
    94                                                   }
    95                                               
    96                                               
    97                                                   //--------RXPOLARITY CONSTRAINT--------
    98                                                   constraint RxPolarity_c {RxPolarity == 0;}

    100                                              
    101                                                  function void post_randomize;
    102             1                       9000           Data_post = MAC_TX_Data;
    103             1                       9000           count_16  = (count_16 + 1) % 3;
    104             1                       9000           count_8   = (count_8 + 1) % 5;
